sequenceDiagram
  participant Trigger as Manual Button / Global Hotkey
  participant Runtime as RuntimeController
  participant Audio as AudioWorker
  participant Interim as Interim Stream Thread
  participant Core as transcriber-core
  participant Post as DefaultPostProcessor
  participant OS as Clipboard + System Events
  participant Bus as Event Bus
  participant UI as Main Window
  participant Overlay as Overlay Window

  Trigger->>Runtime: start_recording(...)
  Runtime->>Audio: start()
  Runtime->>Runtime: phase = recording
  Runtime->>Interim: start_interim_stream()
  Runtime->>Bus: emit state-changed(recording)
  Bus-->>UI: recording state
  Bus-->>Overlay: show recording indicator

  loop Every 1200ms while recording
    Interim->>Audio: snapshot()
    Interim->>Core: transcribe partial audio (timeout 7000ms)
    Core-->>Interim: interim text
    Interim->>Bus: emit interim-transcription frame
    Bus-->>UI: update live preview
  end

  Trigger->>Runtime: stop_recording_and_transcribe(...)
  Runtime->>Audio: stop()
  Runtime->>Runtime: phase = transcribing
  Runtime->>Bus: emit state-changed(transcribing)
  Runtime->>Core: transcribe full capture (timeout 90000ms)
  Core-->>Runtime: transcript + model metadata
  Runtime->>Post: clean trailing artifacts
  Post-->>Runtime: final text

  Runtime->>OS: capture focus anchor + clipboard snapshot (optional)
  Runtime->>OS: write transcript to clipboard

  alt Focus unchanged
    Runtime->>OS: trigger Cmd+V via osascript
  else Focus drift or focus check failed
    Runtime->>Runtime: skip paste for safety
  end

  opt Clipboard policy = restore_previous
    Runtime->>OS: restore previous clipboard text
  end

  Runtime->>Runtime: phase = idle
  Runtime->>Bus: emit transcription-complete + state-changed(idle)
  Bus-->>UI: render final transcript + metadata
  Bus-->>Overlay: hide overlay
